node.text:
With an Attitude of gratitude and @sblabeauty ‘s peptides and actives like Hyaluronic Acid Complex which delivers lipids which replenish moisture, plumps skin cells, reduces lines and wrinkles and visibly tightens the skin.
And Our SBLA Proprietary Double Peptide Blend which increases collagen production, reduces lines & wrinkles, and increases skin firmness.
Skin Repair & Brightening Blend containing Acetyl Glucosamine (Amino Acid) to moisturize, brighten & even out skin tone, repairs & treats sun damage ( hello!) while reducing age spots. 🙌🏼I’ll drink to that! Cheers! 
It also reduces puffiness & inflammation as well as tightens and firms loose skin.

See I told you, things are looking up! 
Hope you enjoyed this video which are condensed excerpts from my conversation with @breannenyc during our zoom with @womenatmeredith Thank you I loved chatting with you! 💕

node.text:
It is #selfcaresunday on Friday...because it is never too early to start planning your Sunday self-care routine! 
(And because I forgot to post this last Sunday! 🤦🏼‍♀️)
Check out some of my Sunday staples with @coveteur 💐 they are actually good for any and every day of the week! Here’s to your health‼️❤️
Oh and be sure to stay tuned for my nighttime self care @sblabeauty routine later today!! 🌝 #sbla #sblabeauty #coveteur #selfcare @coveteur @totalgymdirect and the OG #chesterbrinkley (that little leg!)

node.text:
Celebrating 40 years of the iconic American Style of the adorable legend @michaelkors in the chicest garden of hosts extraordinaire Jon and  legs for days @tizzielisch and co hosted by the lovely and glamorously cool @naomiwatts plus strawberry shortcake all on a gorgeous Summer night! Thank you all for including @sailorbrinkleycook and me! PS Thank you @owengould for our new haircuts! 😘💕 
#heresto40more ! At least! ❤️

node.text:
With an Attitude of gratitude and @sblabeauty ‘s peptides and actives like Hyaluronic Acid Complex which delivers lipids which replenish moisture, plumps skin cells, reduces lines and wrinkles and visibly tightens the skin.
And Our SBLA Proprietary Double Peptide Blend which increases collagen production, reduces lines & wrinkles, and increases skin firmness.
Skin Repair & Brightening Blend containing Acetyl Glucosamine (Amino Acid) to moisturize, brighten & even out skin tone, repairs & treats sun damage ( hello!) while reducing age spots. 🙌🏼I’ll drink to that! Cheers! 
It also reduces puffiness & inflammation as well as tightens and firms loose skin.

See I told you, things are looking up! 
Hope you enjoyed this video which are condensed excerpts from my conversation with @breannenyc during our zoom with @womenatmeredith Thank you I loved chatting with you! 💕
